Directed by Badri Venkatesh

Written by G. Radhakrishnan. Badri Venkatesh

Star Santhana Bharathi . M.S. Bhaskar (Captain Kandhasamy / Vazhukkai Kandhasamy (VKS)). G. Marimuthu. Munishkanth. Ramya Nambeeshan. Aadukalam Naren. Rio Raj. Bala Saravanan. Robo Shankar. R.S. Shivaji (Doctor). Anaika Soti. Tiger Thangadurai. Siddharth Vipin

Language Tamil

Producers Rajesh Kumar

Production Positive Print Studios
